Screenshot*

# OS
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Allow specific small files even if pattern matched above
!scripts/utils/*.py
!scripts/**/*.ipynb
!scripts/**/*.js
!config.yaml
!CITATION.cff
!docs/figures/*.png
!docs/figures/*.svg
poster_individual_prompts.md

# --- Public de-identified release IS tracked (overrides *.parquet/*.csv) ---
!data_public/
!data_public/processed/
!data_public/processed/*.parquet
!data_public/processed/*.json
